Package gr.interamerican.bo2.creation.annotations

Annotation Types Summary
ComparableThrough Marks a type as implementing the interface comparable through some its properties.
Delegate2Map Marks a map field for creating delegates to some of its elements.
DelegateMethods Marks a field for creating delegates to some of his methods.
DelegateProperties Marks a field for creating delegates to some of his properties.
DelegateToOtherProperty Marks a class as delegating some of its properties to others.
MockMethods Marks an abstract class as mocking some methods.
MockProperties Marks a class as implementing some properties with mock methods, meaning that the setter will do nothing and the getter will always return null.
Property The purpose of this annotation is to mark fields of a class as properties.
